0.0.1.name: wordpress/clickbank-framework
0.0.1.description:
This plugin provides a handy framework to use for integrating with Clickbank. It will receive all incoming IPN transactions, verify them and then run some custom actions based on the transaction type.

Your can find more comprehensive documentation here Clickbank Framework Documentation
